metadata.name: Lab Cat #0001
metadata.description: Research Lab Cool Cats are a collection of programmatically, randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. The 1st generation consists of 7777 randomly assembled cats from over 99k total options. CCLABs that have a variety of outfits, faces, skeletons and colors - all cats are cool, but golden skeleton cats are the coolest. Each Cool Cat is comprised of a unique body, hat, face and outfit - the possibilities are endless!
